REQUIREMENTS: <br>
Complete trials in Plane of Time A.</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub57.ezboard.com/btetsuyaknights.showUserPublicProfile?gid=klork>Klork</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Guild Leader
